    "description": "Cell Wars is a classic arcade shooter where your goal is to consume all enemy cells by shooting and eating them. Inspired by NES graphics,  gameplay from arcade  80s cabinets, and early 2000s skill tree systems. Unlock abilities and skills to survive waves of regular, elite and boss cells.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGameplay<br />\r\nUpgrade your cell by unlocking new skills in the tech tree.<br />\r\nSteal cells and consume your enemies to gain DNA and purchase upgrades.<br />\r\nBattle against sneaky AI systems. You will need to strategize to defeat synergetic enemies and beefy bosses.<br />\r\nFollow the tech tree branch to build unique cell abilities or branch off and create a custom style of play.<br />\r\nMutations give you and your enemies abilities, so be careful with your choices.<br />\r\nDon't get cocky.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures<br />\r\n<br />\r\n7 enemy types with synergetic abilities and 7 elite equivalents.<br />\r\n28 unlockable skills with branching skill tree paths.<br />\r\n19 mutations that completely change the style of gameplay.<br />\r\n25 levels of increasing difficulty and endless looping gameplay.<br />\r\n3 bosses with unique and creative abilities.",
